adapter.name: DATA_AUD_DynamicMember
adapter.sqlQuery: Select (Case When AuditMemberProperty.DimTypeId = 0 Then 'Entity' When AuditMemberProperty.DimTypeId = 2 Then 'Scenario' When AuditMemberProperty.DimTypeId = 5 Then 'Account' When AuditMemberProperty.DimTypeId = 6 Then 'Flow' When AuditMemberProperty.DimTypeId = 9 Then 'UD1' When AuditMemberProperty.DimTypeId = 10 Then 'UD2' When AuditMemberProperty.DimTypeId = 11 Then 'UD3' When AuditMemberProperty.DimTypeId = 12 Then 'UD4' When AuditMemberProperty.DimTypeId = 13 Then 'UD5' When AuditMemberProperty.DimTypeId = 14 Then 'UD6' When AuditMemberProperty.DimTypeId = 15 Then 'UD7' When AuditMemberProperty.DimTypeId = 16 Then 'UD8' Else 'Unknown' END) AS DimensionType, AuditMemberProperty.DimTypeId, Member.Name, Member.Description, AuditMemberProperty.AuditGuid, AuditMemberProperty.AuditTime, AuditMemberProperty.AuditSeqId, AuditMemberProperty.AuditUser, AuditInsUpdateDel, (Case When AuditInsUpdateDel = 0 Then 'Insert' When AuditInsUpdateDel = 1 Then 'Update' When AuditInsUpdateDel = 2 Then 'Delete' Else 'Unknown' End) As 'Change Type', AuditMemberProperty.MemberId, PrpLkp.OS_PropertyName As PropertyName, AuditMemberProperty.PropertyId, AuditMemberProperty.VaryByCubeTypeId, AuditMemberProperty.VaryByScenarioTypeId, AuditMemberProperty.VaryByTimeId, 'Unknown' As StorageTypeName, AuditMemberProperty.PropStorageTypeId, AuditMemberProperty.DecimalValue, AuditMemberProperty.TextValue, 'Unknown' As PropertyValue From Member INNER Join AuditMemberProperty On Member.DimTypeId = AuditMemberProperty.DimTypeId And Member.MemberId = AuditMemberProperty.MemberId INNER JOIN MDM_Property_LKP PrpLkp ON AuditMemberProperty.DimTypeId = prpLkp.OS_DimTypeID and AuditMemberProperty.PropertyId = PrpLkp.OS_PropertyID Where AuditMemberProperty.dimtypeId = 0 Order By Member.DimTypeId, Member.Name, AuditMemberProperty.PropertyId, AuditMemberProperty.AuditTime DESC

adapter.name: DATA_AuditMemberbyDim_AUD
adapter.sqlQuery: Select (Case When AudMbr.DimTypeID = 0 Then 'Entity' When AudMbr.DimTypeID = 5 Then 'Account' When AudMbr.DimTypeID = 10 Then 'UD2' When AudMbr.DimTypeID = 11 Then 'UD3' When AudMbr.DimTypeID = 12 Then 'UD4' When AudMbr.DimTypeID = 13 Then 'UD5' Else 'Unknown' End) As 'Dimension Type', Dim.Name as 'Dimension Name', AudMbr.Name as 'Member Name', (Case When AuditInsUpdateDel = 0 Then 'Insert' When AuditInsUpdateDel = 1 Then 'Update' When AuditInsUpdateDel = 2 Then 'Delete' Else 'Unknown' End) As 'Change Type', AuditUser as 'User', AuditTime as 'Time' FROM dbo.Member Mbr INNER JOIN dbo.AuditMember AudMbr ON Mbr.DimID = AudMbr.DimID and Mbr.MemberID = AudMbr.MemberID INNER JOIN dbo.Dim ON Mbr.DimID = Dim.DimId

adapter.name: DATA_Validation_Dashboard
adapter.sqlQuery: Select OS_ValidationName as "Validation Name",Dim.Name as Dimension,Count(*) as "Validation Issues" from [dbo].[MDM_ValResults_VAL] Res JOIN [dbo].[MDM_ValConfig_VAL] Conf ON Res.OS_Validation_ID = Conf.OS_Validation_ID JOIN [dbo].[Dim] ON Dim.DimID = Conf.OS_DimID Group By OS_ValidationName,Dim.Name

adapter.name: DATA_ValidationResults_VAL
adapter.sqlQuery: Select MbrDim.Name as [Member Name],HierDim.Name as [Hierarchy Not Included In] FROM [dbo].[MDM_VAL_Results] as VAL JOIN [dbo].Member as MbrDim ON VAL.OS_Member_ID = MbrDim.MemberID JOIN [dbo].Member as HierDim ON VAL.OS_HierNotIn = HierDim.MemberID WHERE VAL.OS_Validation_ID = |!Param_VAL_lbx_Selection!|
